20I%20had%20to%20learn%20on%20the%20fly%20during%20the%20early%20years%20of%20management%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20was%20particularly%20difficult%20because%20I%20was%20younger%20and%20respect%20had%20to%20be%20earned.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Group%20of%20people%20from%20Young%20Master%20Ales%20and%20Dai%20Lee%20Dai%20Pai%20Dong%20in%20Hong%20Kong%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6639d716ec0c696569019f2b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EToby%20To%20Yan%20Choi%20worked%20with%20Hong%20Kong's%20top%20craft%20brewery%2C%20Young%20Master%20Ales.%3Cp%3EToby%20To%20Yan%20Choi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2277278fef-3471-4d11-b9af-8912ecfa8178%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHe's%20hoping%20craft%20beer%20can%20help%20entice%20younger%20diners%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20effort%20to%20infuse%20fresh%20energy%20into%20the%20business%2C%20Choi%20has%20partnered%20with%20local%20beer%20breweries%2C%20such%20as%20Young%20Master%20Ale%2C%20to%20organize%20events%20and%20draw%20in%20a%20younger%20crowd.%20He's%20also%20collaborated%20with%20local%20tour%20companies%20to%20attract%20more%20tourists.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDai%20pai%20dongs%20are%20a%20crucial%20part%20of%20remembering%20and%20preserving%20Hong%20Kong's%20food%20history%20%E2%80%94%20when%20we%20eat%20at%20there%20we%20enjoy%20a%20taste%20of%20the%20past%2C%20and%20help%20ensure%20that%20Cantonese%20culinary%20culture%20continues%20into%20the%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fbettyshanghai%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBetty%20Richardson%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20former%20food%20critic%20who%20moved%20from%20Shanghai%20to%20Hong%20Kong%2C%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BOnce%20these%20dai%20pai%20dong%20are%20gone%2C%20they%20are%20gone%20forever.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E