t%20didn't%20happen.%20And%20later%20on%2C%20when%20Dorsey%20got%20frustrated%20while%20running%20the%20for-profit%20version%20of%20Twitter%2C%20he%20imagined%20that%20Twitter%20could%20help%20start%20an%20independent%2C%20open-source%20protocol%20version%20of%20itself%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbluesky-social-media-app-invite-open-ceo-jay-graber-interview-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBluesky%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20then%20%E2%80%94%20in%20Dorsey's%20telling%20%E2%80%94%20he%20got%20frustrated%20that%20Bluesky%20was%20doing%20things%20like%20the%20old%20Twitter.%20Things%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftechcrunch.com%2F2023%2F07%2F05%2Fbluesky-announces-its-8m-seed-round-first-paid-service-custom-domains%2F%3Fguccounter%3D1%26guce_referrer%3DaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZ29vZ2xlLmNvbS8%26guce_referrer_sig%3DAQAAAG_9mi6lyoAups0ds7S1iOFkfl4Vd7DBDqyKF9irNtpq3pnkLhFPvCUiqncmgluCaaDXbvJEOhGUQR7Q1-Z_hjoY0C-JSWNpdOFvQjHCIyenFIkYYvW0IAwmFwp_WXkjlsJPmS9Enmj_rmz2y0HTzJsRa4Q0GIYh5O1XgbI3sgaW%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eraising%20money%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20moderating%20what%20happened%20on%20its%20platform%2C%20and%20having%20a%20board.%20Which%20Dorsey%20was%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%20Dorsey%20decided%20what%20he%20really%20wanted%20to%20do%20was%20help%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnostr.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENostr%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20another%20Twitter%20alternative%2C%20which%20promises%20to%20%3Cem%3Eactually%3C%2Fem%3E%20be%20an%20open-source%20protocol%2C%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3E%26quot%3BSo%20I%20just%20decided%20to%20delete%20my%20account%20on%20Bluesky%2C%20and%20really%20focus%20on%20Nostr%2C%20and%20funding%20that%20to%20the%20best%20of%20my%20ability.%20I%20asked%20to%20get%20off%20the%20board%20as%20well%2C%20because%20I%20just%20don't%20think%20a%20protocol%20needs%20a%20board%20or%20wants%20a%20board.%20And%20if%20it%20has%20a%2