ternational%20concerns%20about%20the%20rising%20death%20toll%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohn%20Kirby%2C%20the%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20White%20House%20National%20Security%20Council%2C%20told%20reporters%20on%20Thursday%20that%20despite%20the%20single%20shipment%20of%20bombs%20being%20held%20up%2C%20the%20Biden%20administration%20is%20still%20sending%20weapons%20to%20Israel%2C%20which%20is%20getting%20the%20%26quot%3Bvast%2C%20vast%20majority%20of%20everything%20that%20they%20need%20to%20defend%20themselves.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Palestinians%20ride%20on%20a%20vehicle%20as%20they%20flee%20Rafah%20on%20May%209%2C%202024.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663d362af27898f532d5e7ef%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223510%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPalestinians%20ride%20on%20a%20vehicle%20as%20they%20flee%20Rafah%20on%20May%209%2C%202024.%3Cp%3EREUTERS%2FMohammed%20Salem%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20it%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%20how%20Israel%20proceeds%20with%20its%20military%20action%20in%20Rafah%2C%20but%20officials%20have%20been%20defiant%20in%20saying%20that%20they%20will%20continue%20to%20hunt%20down%20Hamas%2C%20regardless%20of%20how%20much%20international%20support%20the%20country%20retains.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20need%20to%20stand%20alone%2C%20we%20will%20stand%20alone%2C%26quot%3B%20Netanyahu%20asserted%20on%20Thursday%2C%20per%20a%20translation.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20said%20that%20if%20necessary%2C%20we%20will%20fight%20with%20our%20fingernails.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-keeps-heavy-firepower-israel-may-change-way-it-fights-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715290797000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663d3497b4abc992e8c7c7f5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%2