22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EExcalibur%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20JDAMs%20was%20that%20their%20reliance%20on%20GNSS%2C%20to%20an%20extent%2C%20was%20supposed%20to%20provide%20a%20level%20of%20precision%2C%26quot%3B%20Withington%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20capability%20and%20accuracy%20of%20those%20much-vaunted%20weapons%20are%20now%20in%20question%2C%20he%20said%2C%20noting%20that%20%26quot%3Bnot%20only%20has%20tactical%20and%20operational%20ramifications%20for%20the%20Ukrainians%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20it%20also%20potentially%20raises%20questions%20about%20%26quot%3Bthe%20wider%20confidence%20others%20have%20in%20those%20systems.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDaniel%20Patt%2C%20a%20senior%20fellow%20at%20the%20Hudson%20Institute%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.congress.gov%2F118%2Fmeeting%2Fhouse%2F116957%2Fwitnesses%2FHHRG-118-AS35-Wstate-PattD-20240313.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Etold%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20Congress%20back%20in%20March%20the%20155mm%20GPS-guided%20Excalibur%20artillery%20shell%20%26quot%3Bhad%20a%2070%25%20efficiency%20rate%20hitting%20targets%20when%20first%20used%20in%20Ukraine%26quot%3B%20but%20%26quot%3Bafter%20six%20weeks%2C%20efficiency%20declined%20to%20only%206%25%20as%20the%20Russians%20adapted%20their%20electronic-warfare%20systems%20to%20counter%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPatt%20added%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20peak%20efficiency%20of%20a%20new%20weapon%20system%20is%20only%20about%20two%20weeks%20before%20countermeasures%20emerge.%26quot%3B%20That%20is%20valuable%20information%20for%20the%20US%20as%20it%20prepares%20for%20potential%20future%20fights.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221240%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Joint%20Direct%20Attack%20Munition%20(JDAMs)%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5a872445d0307229008b48c5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22813%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E2000%20lbs%20GBU-31%20Joint%20Direct%20Attack%20Munitions%20(JDAM)%20are%20transported%20to%20the%20flight%20deck%20of%20USS%20Harry%20S.%20Truman%20(CVN-75).%3Cp%3EUS%20Navy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20has%2C%20as%20a%20defense%20expert%20previously%20told%20BI%2C%20been%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwestern-weapons-wins-against-russia-are-intelligence-bonanza-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bintelligence%20bonanza%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20is%20giving%20the%20US%20an%20opportunity%20to%20learn%20how%20its%20precision%20weapons%20perform%20under%20modern%20threats%20like%20electronic%20warfare.%20It's%20not%20theoretical.%20Instead%2C%20the%20US%20is%20watching%20a%20rival%20power%20engage%20its%20weapons%20in%20a%20real%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIntelligence%20from%20the%20war%20builds%20on%20and%20likely%20advances%20years%20of%20research%20and%20discussion%20among%20US%20defense%20officials%20and%20experts%20about%20how%20electronic%20warfare%20will%20impact%20America's%20arsenal%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-military-china-missile-problem-getting-worse-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egreat%20power%20conflict%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20how%20the%20US%20will%20need%20to%20adapt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECancian%20said%20DoD%20has%20been%20working%20on%20overcoming%20these%20threats%20by%20focusing%20on%20options%20like%20using%20narrower%20signal%20bands%20or%20the%20generation%20of%20stronger%20signals%20that%20are%20able%20to%20burn%20through%20jamming%20attempts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20threats%2C%20nevertheless%2C%20%26quot%3Bremind%20us%20to%20be%20careful%20about%20expecting%20'game%20changers%2C'%20though%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20other%20side%20always%20develops%20countermeasures%20that%20reduce%20effectiveness.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20challenges%2C%20the%20US%20shouldn't%20completely%20write%20off%20its%20precision%20weapons%20should%20it%20one%20day%20find%20itself%20in%20a%20war%20with%20another%20great%20power%2C%20be%20it%20Russia%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-drones-glitching-getting-lost-in-ukraine-picking-chinese-ones-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChina%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20would%20almost%20certainly%20employ%20electronic%20warfare%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithington%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Beven%20if%20that%20jamming%20has%20been%20quite%20successful%2C%20the%20tactical%20imperative%20behind%20this%20is%20to%20work%20out%20a%20way%20to%20outflank%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20that%20electronic%20attack%2C%26quot%3B%20noting%20that%20while%20a%20strong%20Russian%20jamming%20signal%20may%20be%20effective%2C%20it's%20also%20easier%20to%20detect%20and%20destroy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20media%20event%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20Doug%20Bush%2C%20the%20Army's%20acquisition%20chief%2C%20said%20it%20wasn't%20surprising%20Russia%20was%20able%20to%20jam%20US%20weapons.%20He%20said%20it%20was%20part%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bconstant%20cycle%26quot%3B%20of%20innovation%20on%20both%20sides%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20US%20was%20learning%20that%20%26quot%3Bwith%20any%20precision%20weapon%2C%20you%20want%20multiple%20ways%20to%20guide%20it%20to%20its%20target.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20some%20weapons%2C%20that's%20already%20in%20the%20works.%20Earlier%20this%20week%2C%20the%20US%20Air%20Force%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.defense.gov%2FNews%2FContracts%2FContract%2FArticle%2F3765102%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20contract%20for%20add-on%20seekers%20for%20its%20extended-range%20JDAMs%2C%20the%20goal%20being%20to%20improve%20the%20JDAM%20to%20resist%20electronic%20jamming%20and%20instead%20lock%20onto%20the%20source%20of%20the%20jamming%2C%20targeting%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBush%20said%20the%20Army%20had%20created%20a%20team%20focused%20on%20adapting%20its%20weapons%20to%20electronic%20warfare%20issues%20long%20before%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20signaling%20the%20Pentagon's%20clear%20understanding%20of%20the%20problem%20these%20capabilities%20pose.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBush%20previously%20said%20in%20August%202023%20that%20the%20Army%20was%20%26quot%3Bfundamentally%20reinvesting%20in%20rebuilding%20our%20tactical%20electronic-warfare%20capability%20after%20that%20largely%20left%20the%20force%20over%20the%20last%2020%20years%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-russia-war-us-army-urgently-working-on-electronic-warfare-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadded%20%26quot%3Burgency%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20those%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Soldiers%20setting%20up%20portable%20packs.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653fd01e356802a56be7786c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUS%20Army%20electronic-warfare%20specialists%20set%20up%20portable%20packs%20capable%20of%20picking%20up%20and%20jamming%20enemy%20frequencies%20at%20Fort%20Bliss%20in%20Texas%20in%20December%202018.%3Cp%3EStaff%20Sgt.%20Felicia%20Jagdatt%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEfforts%20to%20adapt%20precision%20weapons%20to%20the%20threat%20is%20just%20one%20facet%20of%20a%20multi-layered%20solution%2C%20Withington%20said.%20Other%20solutions%20to%20the%20problem%20involve%20using%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvideo-us-harpoon-missiles-destroy-a-heavily-armed-russian-vessel-in-black-sea-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eother%20weapons%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20prioritizing%20targeting%20the%20point%20of%20origin%20for%20electronic%20warfare%20signals%20early%20in%20a%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20imperative%20that%20forces%20like%20the%20US%20and%20its%20allies%20see%20future%20battle%20in%20a%20case%20that%