lion%20in%20defense%20aid.%20The%20Trump%20White%20House%20disputed%20the%20report%2C%20but%20the%20office%20was%20unmoved%20by%20its%20defense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFaithful%20execution%20of%20the%20law%20does%20not%20permit%20the%20President%20to%20substitute%20his%20own%20policy%20priorities%20for%20those%20that%20Congress%20has%20enacted%20into%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20watchdog%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20unlikely%20that%20Biden%20would%20be%20found%20to%20have%20violated%20the%20law%20if%20the%20White%20House%20spent%20the%20congressionally%20approved%20aid%20on%20Israel%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20fiscal%20year%20in%20September%2C%20according%20to%20a%20defense%20policy%20expert.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20fact%20that%20Congress%20has%20enacted%20money%20to%20support%20Israel%20means%20the%20president%20has%20to%20spend%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Mark%20Cancian%2C%20a%20senior%20advisor%20at%20the%20Washington%20DC-based%20think%20tank%20the%20Center%20for%20Strategic%20and%20International%20Studies%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BSo%20basically%2C%20he's%20going%20to%20have%20to%20spend%20that%20money%20on%20Israel%20as%20Congress%20appropriated%2C%20but%20he%20doesn't%20have%20to%20do%20that%20today.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECancian%20did%20caution%20that%20the%20current%20bomb%20shipment%20Biden%20has%20paused%20likely%20has%20a%20different%20deadline%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20immediately%20clear%20which%20tranche%20of%20money%20that%20falls%20under.%20According%20to%20the%20Council%20on%20Foreign%20Relations%2C%20the%20US%20sends%20roughly%20%243.3%20billion%20to%20Israel%20a%20year%2C%20mostly%20through%20grants%20that%20Israel%20must%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20use%20to%20purchase%20US%20military%20goods%20and%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20it%20wasn't%20just%20about%20the%20letter%20of%20the%20law.%20One%20of%20House%20Democrats'%20impeachment%20articles%20cited%20a%20%26quot%3Bscheme%20or%20course%20of%20conduct%20for%20corrupt%20purposes%20in%20pursuit%20of%20personal%20political%20benefit.%26quot%3B%20Trump's%20withholding%20of%20aid%20wasn't%20the%20offense%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20issue%20was%20whether%20Trump%20took%20official%20action%2C%20delaying%20aid%20to%20benefit%20a%20private%20scheme%20to%20get%20the%20Ukraine%20government%20to%20help%20dig%20up%20dirt%20on%20Hunter%20Biden.%20Trump's%20EU%20ambassador%2C%20Gordon%20Sondland%2C%20later%20confirmed%20a%20quid-pro-quo%20did%20take%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepublicans%20have%20accused%20Biden%20of%20withholding%20weapons%20due%20to%20concerns%20about%20his%20reelection.%20Multiple%20Republicans%20cited%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Farab-americans-uncommitted-michigan-dearborn-biden-israel-gaza-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epresident's%20standing%20in%20Michigan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20key%20swing%20state%2C%20where%20over%20100%2C000%20people%20voted%20%26quot%3Buncommitted%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20state's%20Democratic%20presidential%20primary%20in%20an%20organized%20campaign%20to%20protest%20Biden's%20support%20of%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20is%20it%20on%20hold%3F%20To%20appease%20his%20liberal%20base%20in%20places%20like%20Dearborn%2C%20Michigan%2C%20because%20Joe%20Biden%20is%20in%20trouble%20in%20Michigan%2C%26quot%3B%20Sen.%20Steve%20Daines%20of%20Montana%2C%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20Senate%20GOP's%20campaign%20arm%2C%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBiden%20has%20repeatedly%20expressed%20concern%20about%20civilians%20dying%20during%20the%20war.%20According%20to%20Gaza%20health%20officials%2C%20about%2034%2C000%20people%2C%20many%20of%20them%20women%20and%20children%2C%20have%20been%20killed%20there.%20US%20allies%20%E2%80%94%20the%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20France%2C%20and%20Germany%20%E2%80%94%20have%20all%20expressed%20concern%20about%20an%20invasion%20of%20Rafah.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22aa36f5ec-f426-4624-a00e-709a1dc4086f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E