es%20of%20numerous%20districts%20within%20the%20state%20has%20been%20considered%2C%20including%20Aligarh%2C%20Azamgarh%2C%20Shahjahanpur%2C%20Ghaziabad%2C%20Firozabad%2C%20Farrukhabad%2C%20and%20Moradabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%2C%20after%20assuming%20office%20in%202017%2C%20has%20embarked%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20eradicate%20symbols%20of%20historical%20subjugation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20endeavour%20has%20seen%20numerous%20roads%2C%20parks%2C%20intersections%2C%20and%20buildings%20in%20the%20state%20christened%20in%20the%20honour%20of%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Lucknow%20alone%2C%20one%20can%20traverse%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20Road%2C%20navigate%20through%20Atal%20Chauraha%2C%20access%20the%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20Conference%20Centre%2C%20cross%20Atal%20Setu%2C%20and%20arrive%20at%20Atal%20Bihari%20Kalyan%20Mandap.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20iconic%20Mughalsarai%20railway%20station%2C%20the%20fourth%20busiest%20junction%20in%20the%20country%2C%20underwent%20a%20name%20change%20to%20Deen%20Dayal%20Upadhyay%20Junction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20before%20the%202019%20Kumbh%20Mela%2C%20the%20state%20government%20rechristened%20Allahabad%20to%20Prayagraj%2C%20a%20move%20rooted%20in%20reclaiming%20the%20city's%20historical%20identity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaints%20contend%20that%20the%20original%20name%20of%20this%20historic%20locale%20was%20Prayagraj%2C%20which%20the%20Mughals%20altered%20to%20'Allahabad'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConcurrently%2C%20Faizabad%20was%20renamed%20Ayodhya%2C%20and%20the%20Jhansi%20railway%20station%20was%20also%20renamed%20after%20Rani%20Lakshmi%20Bai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20the%20municipal%20bodies%20of%20Aligarh%20passed%20a%20resolution%20demanding%20the%20city's%20renaming%20to%20Harigarh%2C%20while%20Firozabad%20was%20proposed%20to%20be%20renamed%20Chandra%20Nagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20similar%20proposal%20was%