ndia-news%2Fakbarpur-to-go-yogi-adityanath-hints-at-another-round-of-name-change-in-up-5628190%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fakbarpur-to-go-yogi-adityanath-hints-at-another-round-of-name-change-in-up-5628190%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fakbarpur-to-go-yogi-adityanath-hints-at-another-round-of-name-change-in-up-5628190%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%225%20Indian%20Sailors%20On%20Ship%20Seized%20By%20Iran%20Released%2C%20Departed%20For%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20diplomatic%20breakthrough%2C%20five%20of%20the%20Indian%20sailors%20on%20board%20an%20Israeli-linked%20vessel%20seized%20by%20Tehran%20were%20released%20on%20Thursday%20and%20have%20departed%20from%20Iran%2C%20the%20Indian%20embassy%20in%20Iran%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Embassy%2C%20while%20sharing%20details%20of%20their%20release%2C%20thanked%20the%20Iranian%20authorities%20for%20their%20close%20coordination%20with%20the%20Embassy%20and%20Indian%20Consulate%20in%20Bandar%20Abbas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B5%20of%20the%20Indian%20sailors%20on%20MSC%20Aries%20have%20been%20released%20and%20departed%20from%20Iran%20today%20evening.%20We%20appreciate%20the%20Iranian%20authorities%20for%20their%20close%20coordination%20with%20the%20Embassy%20and%20Indian%20Consulate%20in%20Bandar%20Abbas%2C%26quot%3B%20MEA%20official%20spokesperson%20Randhir%20Jaiswal%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israel-linked%20cargo%20ship%20was%20seized%20by%20Iran%20on%20April%2013%2C%20with%2017%20Indian%20nationals%20onboard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIran's%20Islamic%20Revolutionary%20Guard%20Corps%20Navy%20seized%20the%20container%20ship%20near%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz%20and%20MSC%20Aries%20was%20last%20seen%20on%20April%2012%2C%20sailing%20towards%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20Dubai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Ann%20Tessa%20Joseph%20from%20Thrissur%2C%20Kerala%2C%20one%20of%20the%2017%20Indian%20crew%20members%20of%20the%20Israel-linked%20cargo%20ship%20'MSC%20Aries'%20that%20was%20seized%20by%20Iran%20on%20April%2013%2C%20returned%20safely%20to%20her%20homeland%20on%20April%2018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20had%20also%20said%20that%20one%20of%20the%2017%20Indian%20crew%20members%20has%20safely%20returned%20to%20India%20and%20others%20are%20safe%2C%20adding%20that%20they%20will%20be%20released%20once%20their%20contractual%20obligations%20are%20accomplished.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20girl%20who%20was%20there%20has%20returned.%20We%20had%20asked%20for%20consular%20access%20for%20these%2016%20people%20and%20we%20received%20that%20and%20our%20officers%20met%20them.%20Their%20health%20is%20good%20and%20there%20is%20no%20problem%20of%20any%20kind%20on%20the%20ship.%20Concerning%20their%20return%2C%20there%20are%20some%20technicalities%20and%20contractual%20obligations.%20Once%20they%20are%20done%2C%20it%20will%20decide%20their%20return%2C%26quot%3B%20MEA%20spokesperson%2C%20Randhir%20Jaiswal%20said%20in%20a%20weekly%20press%20briefing%20on%20April%2025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Iranian%20Ambassador%20to%20India%2C%20Iraj%20Elahi%2C%20has%20also%20said%20that%20the%20Indian%20nationals%2C%20crew%20members%20of%20MSC%20Aries%2C%20are%20not%20detained%20and%20that%20they%20are%20free%20to%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20seizure%20of%20the%20container%20vessel%2C%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20spoke%20to%20his%20Iranian%20counterpart%20Hossein%20Amir-Abdollahian%2C%20bringing%20up%20the%20release%20of%20the%2017%20Indian%20crew%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20the%20request%20of%20the%20Estonian%20side%20regarding%20the%20Portuguese%20ship%20seized%20in%20the%20territorial%20waters%20of%20Iran%20and%20the%20release%20of%20the%20crew%2C%20Amirabdollahian%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20ship%2C%20