est%2C%20Dr%20Pemmasani%20said%20it%20was%20about%20giving%20back%20to%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20need%20to%20come%20because%20I%20have%20probably%20all%20the%20comforts%20that%20anybody%20could%20ask%20for%20in%20this%20world.%20The%20reason%20I%20came%20is%20mainly%20because%20of%20I%20want%20to%20give%20it%20back%20to%20the%20society...%20Once%20you%20have%20that%20ideology%2C%20you%20can%20patiently%20listen%20to%20most%20human%20problems%20and%20solve%20most%20of%20them...%20As%20an%20entrepreneur%2C%20you%20know%20how%20to%20prioritise%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20graduate%20from%20Osmania%20Medical%20College%2C%20Dr%20Pemmasani%20worked%20in%20Johns%20Hopkins%20University%20-%20Sinai%20Hospital%20in%20the%20US%20for%20five%20years.%20Back%20in%20India%2C%20he%20turned%20an%20educationist%20and%20entrepreneur%20before%20deciding%20to%20plunge%20into%20politics.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20campaign%2C%20he%20insists%2C%20is%20not%20negative.%20%26quot%3BThe%20state%20is%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20debt.%20We%20don't%20have%20capital%20we%20don't%20have.%20We%20don't%20have%20a%20single%20industry.%20So%20we%20need%20the%20support%20of%20the%20central%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20party%20aims%20to%20restore%20permissions%20to%20the%20130%20institutes%20that%20Mr%20Naidu%20had%20allowed%20when%20he%20was%20the%20Chief%20Minister.%20%26quot%3BJagan%20Mohan%20Reddy%20completely%20cancelled%20all%20130%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20which%20is%20why%20now%20these%20institutes%20have%20to%20take%20individual%20permissions%20when%20they%20come%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20two-%20to%20three-year%20process%20even%20to%20request%E2%80%A6%20For%20somebody%20to%20come%20and%20create%20a%20project%20report%2C%20building%20some%20infrastructure.%20Creating%20a%20job%20will%20take%20two%20to%20three%20years.%20I'm%20telling%20everybody%20we%20can't%20give%20you%20a%20job%20