0Not%20Permit%20Research%20By%20Chinese%20Vessel%20In%20Our%20Waters%3A%20Maldives%20Minister%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EEmphasising%20that%20%26quot%3Bpeace%20and%20security%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20is%20important%20for%20countries%20in%20the%20neighbourhood%20including%20India%2C%20Maldivian%20Foreign%20Minister%20Moosa%20Zameer%20on%20Thursday%20said%20that%20his%20government%20has%20%26quot%3Bnot%20permitted%20the%20Chinese%20vessel%26quot%3B%20for%20research%20purposes%20in%20the%20Maldivian%20waters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20by%20the%20Maldivian%20Foreign%20Minister%20came%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20Chinese%20marine%20research%20vessel%20Xiang%20Yang%20Hong%203%20returning%20to%20Maldivian%20waters%2C%20marking%20its%20second%20visit%20to%20the%20archipelago%20nation%20within%20two%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20peace%20and%20security%20of%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20is%20important%20for%20both%20India%20and%20Maldives%20and%20Sri%20Lanka%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20countries%20that%20we%20have%20in%20the%20neighbourhood.%20So%2C%20we%20will%20continue%20to%20work%20together%20as%20I%20said%20earlier%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20the%20port%20call%20for%20Chinese%20vessels%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOur%20government%20issued%20personal%20rotation%20and%20friendly%20portable%20permits%2C%20and%20diplomatic%20clearances%20came%20from%20the%20Chinese%20side%2C%20which%20is%20very%20common%20in%20Maldives.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20that's%20how%20it%20has%20happened%20we%20as%20a%20peaceful%20country%2C%20welcome%20those%20vessels%20which%20come%20for%20peaceful%20purposes.%20But%20they%20didn't%20come%20for%20research%20in%20the%20Maldivian%20waters%2C%20we%20have%20not%20permitted%20the%20Chinese%20vessel%20for%20research%20in%20the%20Maldivian%20waters%2C%26quot%3B%20Maldivian%20Foreign%20Minister%20Moosa%20Zameer%20said%20while%20maintaining%20that%20research%20vessels%20are%20not%20welcome%20in%20the%20Maldivian%20waters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20April%2027%2C%20Chinese%20marine%20research%20vessel%20Xiang%20Yang%20Hong%203%20returned%20to%20Maldivian%20waters%2C%20marking%20its%20second%20visit%20to%20the%20archipelago%20nation%20within%20two%20months%20after%20Pro-China%20Maldives%20President%20Mohamed%20Muizzu's%20ruling%20People's%20National%20Congress%20(PNC)%20won%20the%20Parliamentary%20elections%2C%20as%20reported%20by%20Adhadhu%20news%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20pertinent%20to%20note%20that%20Defence%20Minister%20Ghassan%20Maumoon%20last%20month%20told%20the%20Maldivian%20Parliament%20that%20the%20Chinese%20vessel%20would%20not%20conduct%20any%20research%20despite%20sailing%20inside%20and%20near%20Maldivian%20waters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20no%20permission%20given%20to%20conduct%20any%20research%20in%20the%20Maldives%20territory.%20After%20docking%20in%20Male'%20and%20buying%20food%2C%20they%20did%20a%20crew%20change.%20People%20who%20came%20on%20an%20airplane%20went%20board%20the%20boat%20and%20those%20on%20the%20boat%20left%20via%20the%20airplane.%20That%20was%20the%20permission%20that%20was%20given%2C%26quot%3B%20Adhadhu%20quoted%20Mr%20Maumoon%20as%20saying%20on%20March%2025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERelations%20between%20India%20and%20the%20Maldives%20have%20been%20strained%20since%20President%20Muizzu%20took%20office%20in%20November%2C%20shifting%20the%20government's%20focus%20towards%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715278920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F5nijbjec_chinse-ship_625x300_22_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdid-not-permit-research-by-chinese-vessel-in-our-waters-maldives-minister-5628078%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Emphasising%20that%20%26quot%3Bpeace%20and%20security%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20is%20important%2C%20Maldivian%20Foreign%20Minister%20