indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fwhat-is-happening-with-aid-at-gazas-crossings%2Farticleshow%2F109989073.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F109989073.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fwhat-is-happening-with-aid-at-gazas-crossings%2Farticleshow%2F109989073.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fwhat-is-happening-with-aid-at-gazas-crossings%2Famp_articleshow%2F109989073.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fwhat-is-happening-with-aid-at-gazas-crossings%2Famp_articleshow%2F109989073.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22No%20New%20Mining%20In%20Aravallis%20In%20Delhi%2C%203%20States%20Till%20Further%20Orders%3A%20Top%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20important%20order%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20asked%20Delhi%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20Gujarat%20to%20not%20give%20any%20new%20mining%20permissions%20in%20the%20Aravallis%20until%20further%20directions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStriking%20a%20balance%20between%20protecting%20the%20environment%20and%20the%20livelihood%20of%20the%20people%20engaged%20in%20mining%20activities%2C%20the%20court%20stressed%2C%20however%2C%20that%20its%20order%20will%20not%20in%20any%20way%20be%20construed%20as%20a%20stay%20on%20mining%20already%20being%20carried%20out%20in%20the%20range%20with%20valid%20permits%20and%20licences.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Haryana%20government%20had%20sought%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20approval%20to%20begin%20mining%20in%20the%20Aravallis%20in%20Gurugram%20and%20Faridabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20of%20Justices%20B%20R%20Gavai%20and%20A%20S%20Oka%20said%20all%20states%20that%20are%20home%20to%20the%20Aravalli%20range%20will%20be%20free%20to%20consider%20and%20process%20applications%20and%20renewals%20for%20grant%20of%20mining%20leases%2C%20but%20cannot%20grant%20final%20permission%20without%20the%20court's%20nod.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20pointed%20out%20that%20illegal%20mining%20was%20a%20big%20issue%20in%20the%20Aravallis%20and%20said%20that%20different%20states%20had%20different%20definitions%20of%20the%20Aravalli%20hills%20and%20range.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20a%20report%20submitted%20by%20the%20Central%20Empowered%20Committee%20had%20pointed%20to%20various%20illegal%20mining%20activities%20being%20carried%20out%20across%20the%20state%20of%20Rajasthan%20and%20had%20also%20given%20district-wise%20details.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20that%20the%20issue%20related%20to%20mining%20activities%20in%20the%20Aravalli%20Hills%20needs%20to%20be%20jointly%20addressed%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Environment%2C%20Forest%20and%20Climate%20Change%20as%20well%20as%20all%20the%20four%20states%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Set%20Up%20Panel'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20ordered%20the%20setting%20up%20of%20a%20committee%20to%20prepare%20a%20uniform%20definition%20of%20the%20Aravalli%20Hills%20and%20range.%20The%20panel%2C%20which%20has%20been%20asked%20to%20submit%20a%20report%20within%20two%20months%2C%20will%20consist%20of%20the%20secretary%20of%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Environment%2C%20Forest%20and%20Climate%20Change%2C%20forest%20secretaries%20of%20the%20four%20states%20and%20one%20representative%20each%20from%20the%20Forest%20Survey%20of%20India%20and%20the%20Central%20Empowered%20Committee.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20clarified%20that%20ongoing%20mining%20activities%20will%20remain%20unaffected%20and%20current%20auction%20processes%20will%20not%20be%20interrupted.%20It%20said%20the%2