es-resumption-of-work-124050900928_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20airline%2C%20which%20cancelled%2085%20flights%20on%20Thursday%2C%20is%20receiving%20help%20from%20its%20parent%20company%2C%20Air%20India%2C%20which%20is%20operating%20flights%20on%2020%20of%20its%20routes%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fai-express-withdraws-terminations-union-assures-resumption-of-work-124050900928_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fai-express-withdraws-terminations-union-assures-resumption-of-work-124050900928_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fai-express-withdraws-terminations-union-assures-resumption-of-work-124050900928_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Reservation%20In%20Focus%20After%20PM%20Panel's%20Findings%20On%20Minorities%2C%20Says%20Minister%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUnion%20minister%20Rajeev%20Chandrasekhar%20has%20said%20the%20ramifications%20of%20a%20new%20population%20study%2C%20which%2C%20among%20other%20things%2C%20found%20the%20Muslim%20community%20growing%20exponentially%2C%20have%20to%20be%20studied%20from%20various%20angles%20to%20determine%20its%20fallouts.%20The%20most%20crucial%20of%20these%20would%20be%20the%20question%20of%20reservation%20in%20jobs%20and%20education%2C%20especially%20in%20terms%20of%20other%20beneficiaries.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20one%20minority%20community%20grows%2C%20there%20is%20a%20question%20of%20how%20it%20affects%20other%20minority%20communities%20in%20terms%20of%20opportunities%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20one%20minority%20community%20grows%20so%20fast%2C%20so%20much%20faster%20than%20other%20minority%20communities%2C%20is%20there%20a%20risk%20that%20the%20other%20minority%20communities%3F%20Like%20Parsis%20and%20Jains%20and%20Buddhists%20and%20Sikhs%20and%20Christians%20are%20crowded%20out%20from%20the%20benefits%20and%20the%20schemes%20designed%20for%20minorities%3F%20From%20education%2C%20from%20jobs%20and%20opportunities%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20minister%20told%20NDTV%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20there%20would%20be%20the%20question%20of%20other%20deserving%20communities%2C%20like%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%2C%20which%20have%20been%20denied%20the%20same%20benefits%20for%20decades%2C%20especially%20when%20seen%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20Congress%20%26quot%3Btalking%20about%20going%20against%20the%20constitution%20and%20giving%20that%20same%20community%20more%20reservations%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20data%20from%20the%20Economic%20Advisory%20Council%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20showed%20the%20Hindu%20population%20has%20decreased%20by%207.82%20per%20cent%20between%201950%20and%202015%20in%20India.%20The%20population%20of%20Muslims%20has%20increased%20by%2043.15%20per%20cent%20in%20the%20same%20period%2C%20suggesting%20there%20is%20a%20conducive%20environment%20in%20the%20country%20to%20foster%20diversity%2C%20the%20panel%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20findings%20are%20in%20line%20with%20the%20situation%20in%20developed%20nations%20in%20Europe%20where%20the%20number%20of%20minorities%20have%20grown%2C%20mostly%20through%20migration%20and%20conversion.%20The%20majority%20communities%20have%20experienced%20a%20negative%20growth%2C%20especially%20in%20nations%20like%20France.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20said%20the%20reasons%20for%20India%20--%20where%20illegal%20migration%20and%20conversion%20both%20happen%20--%20have%20to%20be%20examined.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20general%20election%2C%20the%20paper%20has%20sparked%20controversy.%20The%20question%20of%20reservation%20has%20been%20mainstreamed%20into%20a%20huge%20election%20issue%2C%20with%20the%20Opposition%20alleging%20that%20if%20the%20BJP%20comes%20to%20power%20for%20a%20third%20term%2C%20they%20would%20scrap%20reservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20allegations%20of%20%26quot%3Bscare-mongering%26quot%3B%2C%20Mr%20Chandrasekhar%20said%20timing%20is%20immaterial%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20facts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20particularly%20don't%20feel%20that%20when%20there%20is%20some%20truth%20that%20is%20put%20out%20there%2C%20data%20and%20facts%20that%20are%20put%20out%20there%2C%20whether%20it%20is%20during%20election%2C%20before%20election%20or%20after%20election%20facts%20remain%20the%20facts%2C%20the%20truth%20remains%20the%20truth.%20And%20there%20is%20no%20way%20of%20people%20trying%20to%20wriggle%20out%20of%20an%20uncomfortable%20truth%20and%20to%20find%20a%20more%20convenient%20truth%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20paper%20said%20the%20population%20trend%20for%20Muslims%20is%20%26quot%3Bparticularly%20remarkable%26quot%3B%20given%20the%20wider%20context%20within%20the%20South%20Asian%20neighborhood%2C%20%26quot%3Bwhere%20the%20share%20of%20the%20majority%20religious%20denomination%20has%20increased%20and%20minority%20populations%20have%20shrunk%20alarmingly%20across%20countries%20like%20Bangladesh%2C%20Pakistan%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20Bhutan%20and%20Afghanistan%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20paper%20said%20it%20is%20not%20surprising%20that%20minority%20populations%20from%20across%20the%20neighborhood%20come%20to%20India%20during%20times%20of%20duress.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715276100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F6j17mfr8_rajeev-chandrasekhar-650_625x300_31_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Freservation-in-focus-after-pm-panels-findings-on-minorities-says-union-minister-rajeev-chandrasekhar-5627155%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Union%20minister%20Rajeev%20Chandrasekhar%20today%20said%20the%20ramifications%20of%20a%2