5Cn%3Cp%3EConciliation%20proceedings%20were%20held%20at%20the%20Labour%20Commissioner's%20office%20on%20Thursday%20and%20representatives%20of%20the%20airline's%20management%20and%20the%20Air%20India%20Express%20Employees%20Union%20attended.%20A%20document%20was%20signed%20during%20the%20meeting%2C%20which%20has%20been%20accessed%20by%20NDTV.%20Bearing%20the%20masthead%20of%20the%20Chief%20Labour%20Commissioner%20(Central)%2C%20it%20was%20signed%20by%20representatives%20of%20both%20the%20management%20and%20the%20union.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20reported%20by%20the%20media%20that%20the%20cabin%20crew%20of%20Air%20India%20Express%20Ltd.%20have%20reported%20sick-en-masse%20which%20disrupted%20flight%20operations%20widely...%20After%20detailed%20discussions%20deliberation%2C%20persuasion%20and%20on%20appeal%20of%20Conciliation%20Officer%20and%20Chief%20Labour%20Commissioner%20(Central)%20the%20representative%20of%20union%20(members%20of%20cabin%20crew)%20agreed%20that%20all%20the%20cabin%20crew%20members%20who%20have%20reported%20sick%20will%20report%20for%20duty%20with%20fitness%20certificate%20immediately%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20document%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20appeal%20of%20the%20Chief%20Labour%20Commissioner%20(Central)%20the%20management%20agreed%20to%20reinstate%2025%20cabin%20crew%20who%20have%20been%20terminated%20on%2007th%20and%2008th%20May%202024%20for%20reporting%20sick%20as%20a%20concerted%20action%20immediately.%20The%20management%20will%20review%20the%20cases%20of%20these%20cabin%20crew%20as%20per%20service%20regulations%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Labour%20Commissioner's%20office%20said%20that%20the%20representatives%20of%20the%20management%20have%20given%20an%20assurance%20that%20all%20the%20issues%20raised%20by%20the%20cabin%20crew%20before%20them%20and%20during%20conciliation%20proceedings%20would%20be%20looked%20into%20and%20resolved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%20on%20Thursday%2C%20the%20airline%20issued%20letters%20to%20the%20sacked%20employees%20stating%20that%20they%20were%20being%20reinstated%20with%20immediate%20effect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPursuant%20to%20the%20conciliation%20proceedings%20dated%2009.05.2024%2C%20it%20has%20been%20decided%20to%20reinstate%20you%20in%20the%20services%20with%20immediate%20effect.%20Above%20is%20without%20prejudice%20to%20our%20rights%20to%20review%20your%20case%20as%20per%20the%20Service%20Regulations%20as%20mentioned%20in%20the%20minutes%20of%20conciliation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20letter%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20stated%20that%20the%20month's%20salary%20credited%20to%20the%20employees'%20accounts%20after%20the%20termination%20letter%20was%20issued%20would%20be%20adjusted%20against%20the%20salary%20payable%20for%20May.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20breakthrough%20will%20come%20as%20a%20relief%20to%20passengers%2C%20hundreds%20of%20whom%20were%20left%20stranded%2C%20especially%20on%20Wednesday%20when%20the%20sudden%20cancellations%20began.%20Air%20India%20Express%20CEO%20Aloke%20Singh%20had%20written%20to%20employees%20on%20Wednesday%20and%20said%20that%20the%20number%20of%20flights%20being%20operated%20will%20be%20reduced%20over%20the%20next%20few%20days%2C%20but%20all%20cabin%20crew%20members%20are%20expected%20to%20return%20to%20work%20immediately%20and%20services%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20normalised%20in%20three-four%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E'Happy%20With%20Progress'%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20Air%20India%20Express%20spokesperson%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20pleased%20with%20the%20progress%20we%20made%20at%20the%20conciliation%20meeting%20and%20welcome%20our%20cabin%20crew%20colleagues%20back%20at%20work.%20This%20will%20help%20us%20swiftly%20restore%20our%20flight%20schedule%20and%20fulfil%20our%20commitments%20to%20our%20guests.%20We%20sincerely%20apologise%20to%20those%20inconvenienced%20by%20these%20unintended%20disruptions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20we%20gradually%20bring%20our%20operations%20back%20to%20normalcy%2C%20we%20urge%20our%20guests%20booked%20to%20fly%20with%20us%20to%20check%20their%20flight%20status%20before%20heading%20to%20the%20airport.%20If%20their%20flight%20is%20cancelled%2C%20or%20delayed%20beyond%203%20hours%2C%20they%20may%20opt%20for%20a%20full%20refund%20or%20reschedule%20to%20a%20later%20date%20without%20any%20fees%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20airline%20had%20to%20cancel%20flights%20after%20300%20senior%20cabin%20crew%20members%20began%20reporting%20sick%20at%20the%20last%20minute%20starting%20Tuesday%20night%20and%20then%20switched%20off%20their%20cellphones.%20What%20precipitated%20the%20crisis%20were%20new%20employment%20terms%20and%20modifications%20in%20the%20compensation%20package%2C%20sources%20had%20said.%20Crew%20members%20had%20also%20alleged%20a%20lack%20of%20equality%20in%20the%20treatment%20of%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20had%20come%20to%20light%20on%20Thursday%20that%20the%20airline%20had%20sacked%2025%20of%20the%20crew%20members%20who%20had%20called%20in%20sick.%20The%20others%20said%20they%20would%20not%20return%20to%20work%20until%20they%20were%20reinstated.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715275260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F1o54v3jg_air-india-express-650-_650x400_09_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbreakthrough-in-air-india-express-crisis-terminated-workers-will-be-reinstated-5626458%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20major%20breakthrough%20in%20the%20Air%20India%20Express%20crisis%2C%20the%20airline's%20management%20has%20sent%20letters%20reinstating%20all%2025%20crew%20members%20who%20had%20been%20sacked%20for%20taking%20part%20in%20the%20'mass%20leave'%20protests.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbreakthrough-in-air-india-express-crisis-terminated-workers-will-be-reinstated-5626458%