ty%2C%20and%20cultures.%26quot%3B%20If%20the%20schedule%20goes%20as%20planned%2C%20iSpace%20plans%20to%20deploy%20the%20memory%20disc%20on%20its%20Resilience%20lunar%20lander%20as%20part%20of%20its%20Hakuto-R%20Mission%202%20and%20deliver%20it%20to%20the%20moon%20sometime%20in%20late%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJulien%20Lamamy%2C%20CEO%20of%20ispace-Europe%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20%26quot%3BMaintaining%20linguistic%20diversity%20and%20preserving%20culture%20are%20significant%20aspects%20of%20UNESCO's%20mandate.%20We%20are%20very%20honoured%20to%20announce%20that%20ispace's%20Hakuto-R%20Mission%202%20will%20contribute%20to%20realise%20UNESCO's%20lunar%20mission%20to%20benefit%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20continue%20to%20progress%20on%20Hakuto-R%20Mission%202%2C%20with%20the%20recent%20lander%20and%20rover%20development%20achievements%20that%20put%20us%20on%20a%20timeline%20for%20a%20winter%202024%20launch%20carrying%20UNESCO's%20payload%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20Japanese%20company's%20first%20moon%20lander%20named%20Hakuto-R%20was%20launched%20in%20December%202022%20on%20the%20Mission-1.%20On%20April%2025%2C%202023%2C%20the%20lander%20made%20a%20landing%20attempt%2C%20however%2C%20the%20spacecraft%20crashed%20because%20the%20onboard%20computer%20miscalculated%20the%20altitude.%20Hakuto-R%20Mission%202%2C%20the%20company's%20second%20mission%2C%20will%20be%20launched%20this%20year%20and%20will%20also%20include%20%26quot%3Ba%20micro%20moon%20rover%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715268000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fejrgj88g_hakutor-mission-2_625x300_09_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fprivate-moon-lander-will-carry-memory-disk-of-275-languages-this-year-5627008%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20move%20is%20seen%20as%20an%20attempt%20to%20save%20a%20portion%20of%20human%20history%20in%20the%20e