n.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkedarnath-gangotri-yamnotri-shrines-to-open-for-devotees-from-tomorrow-5626448%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkedarnath-gangotri-yamnotri-shrines-to-open-for-devotees-from-tomorrow-5626448%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Man%20Goes%20Live%20On%20Insta%20Inside%20Gujarat%20Polling%20Station%2C%20Repolling%20Ordered%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20(EC)%20has%20ordered%20fresh%20voting%20on%20May%2011%20at%20a%20polling%20station%20under%20the%20Dahod%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20in%20Gujarat%20from%20where%20a%20man%20live-streamed%20voting%20on%20May%207%2C%20the%20video%20of%20which%20went%20viral%2C%20an%20official%20said%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFour%20election%20officials%2C%20including%20a%20presiding%20officer%2C%20an%20assistant%20presiding%20officer%20and%20two%20polling%20officers%20as%20well%20a%20police%20constable%20were%20suspended%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20incident%2C%20the%20office%20of%20the%20Gujarat%20Chief%20Electoral%20Officer%20(CEO)%20said%20in%20a%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ECI%20declared%20null%20and%20void%20the%20voting%20which%20took%20place%20at%20Parthampur%20polling%20station%20at%20Santrampur%20taluka%20in%20Mahisagar%20district%20after%20taking%20into%20account%20a%20report%20submitted%20by%20the%20Returning%20Officer%20and%20Observer%20regarding%20irregularities%2C%20the%20CEO%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20soon%20as%20the%20irregularities%20were%20reported%2C%20the%20CEO%20sought%20a%20report%20from%20the%20RO%20regarding%20the%20incident%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20was%20sent%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%2C%20which%20under%20section%2058%2C%20sub-section%202%20of%20the%20Representation%20of%20the%20People%20Act%2C%20declared%20the%20polling%20held%20at%20the%20polling%20station%20on%20May%207%20as%20null%20and%20void.%20A%20fresh%20polling%20has%20been%20scheduled%20at%20the%20polling%20station%20between%207%20am%20and%206%20pm%20on%20May%2011%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20presiding%20officer%2C%20assistant%20presiding%20officer%2C%20two%20polling%20officers%20and%20one%20police%20constable%20have%20been%20suspended%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20incident%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%2026%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20polling%20was%20held%20in%2025%20constituencies%20on%20Tuesday%20in%20the%20third%20phase%20of%20the%20general%20elections.%20The%20BJP%20candidate%20in%20Surat%20has%20won%20unopposed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20had%20lodged%20a%20complaint%20with%20the%20EC%20about%20%26quot%3Bbooth%20capturing%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bbogus%20voting%26quot%3B%20by%20submitting%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20viral%20video%2C%20and%20demanded%20repolling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%2C%20Vijay%20Bhabhor%2C%20had%20stayed%20in%20the%20polling%20booth%20for%20five%20minutes%2C%20during%20which%20he%20went%20live%20on%20Instagram%20and%20also%20allegedly%20cast%20votes%20on%20behalf%20of%20two%20other%20electors%2C%20resorting%20to%20bogus%20voting%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrabha%20Taviad%20is%20the%20Congress%20candidate%20in%20the%20constituency.%20She%20is%20pitted%20against%20incumbent%20MP%20Jasvantsinh%20Bhabhor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20claimed%20that%20the%20person%20who%20relayed%20the%20%26quot%3Bbooth%20capturing%26quot%3B%20video%20on%20Instagram%20is%20the%20son%20of%20a%20local%20BJP%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20video%20shows%20Vijay%20Bhabhor%20purportedly%20focusing%20the%20camera%20on%20EVM%20(electronic%20voting%20machine)%20and%20VVPAT%20(voter%20verifiable%20paper%20audit%20trail)%20machine%20and%20seeking%20five%20to%20ten%20minutes%20from%20a%20poll%20official%20even%20when%20he%20is%20asked%20to%20leave.%20Bhabhor%20purportedly%20also%20says%20that%20%26quot%3Bonly%20the%20BJP%20works%20here%26quot%3B.%20His%20accomplice%20was%20also%20seen%20in%20the%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20machine%20belongs%20to%20my%20father.%20Only%20one%20thing%20works%20-%20that%20is%20BJP%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Bhabhor%20before%20pressing%20a%20button%20on%20the%20EVM%2C%20as%20per%20the%20video.%20%26quot%3BOnly%20Vijay%20Bhabhor%20works%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20purportedly%20says.%20He%20was%20later%20detained%20on%20the%20charge%20of%20bogus%20voting.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715263800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-12%2Felection-commission-of-india_650x400_61513230434.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-polls-2024-man-goes-live-on-instagram-inside-gujarat-dahod-polling-station-eci-orders-repolling-5626511%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Election%20Commission%20(EC)%20has%20ordered%20fresh%20voting%20on%20May%2011%20at%20a%20polling%20station%20under%20the%20Dahod%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20in%20Gujarat%20from%20where%20a%20man%20live-streamed%20voting%20on%20May%207%2C%20the%20video%20of%20which%20went%20viral%2C%20an%20official%20said%20Thursday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-polls-2024-man-goes-live-on-instagram-inside-gujarat-dahod-polling-station-eci-orders-repolling-5626511%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-polls-2024-man-goes-live-on-instagram-inside-gujarat-dahod-polling-station-eci-orders-repolling-5626511%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-polls-2024-man-goes-live-on-instagram-inside-gujarat-dahod-polling-station-eci-orders-repolling-5626511%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Top%20Medical%20Body's%20Advisory%20Urges%20People%20To%20Avoid%20Protein%20Supplements%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Council%20of%20Medical%20Research%20has%20pressed%20for%20avoiding%20protein%20supplements%20for%20building%20body%20mass%20and%20has%20recommended%20restricting%20salt%20intake%2C%20minimising%20sugar%20and%20ultra-processed%20foods%20and%20reading%20information%20on%20food%20labels%20to%20make%20informed%20and%20healthy%20food%20choices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hyderabad-based%20National%20Institute%20of%20Nutrition%20(NIN)%20under%20the%20top%20health%20research%20body%20on%20Wednesday%20released%20revised%20'Dietary%20Guidelines%20for%20Indians%20(DGIs)'%20to%20meet%20the%20requirements%20of%20essential%20nutrients%20and%20prevent%20non-communicable%20diseases%20(NCDs).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DGIs%20have%20been%20drafted%20by%20a%20multi-disciplinary%20committee%20of%20experts%20led%20by%20Dr%20Hemalatha%20R%2C%20Director%2C%20ICMR-NIN%20and%20have%20undergone%20several%20scientific%20reviews.%20Seventeen%20guidelines%20have%20been%20listed%20in%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20DGIs%2C%20the%20NIN%20stated%20that%20prolonged%20intake%20of%20large%20amounts%20of%20protein%20powders%20or%20consumption%20of%20high%20protein%20concentrate%20has%20been%20associated%20with%20potential%20dangers%20such%20as%20bone%20mineral%20loss%20and%20kidney%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20stated%20that%20sugar%20should%20be%20less%20than%205%20per%20cent%20of%20total%20energy%20intake%20and%20a%20balanced%20diet%20should%20provide%20not%20more%20than%2045%20per%20cent%20calories%20from%20cereals%2C%20and%20millets%20and%20up%20to%2015%20per%20cent%20of%20calories%20from%20pulses%2C%20beans%20and%20meat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rest%20of%20the%20calories%20should%20come%20from%20nuts%2C%20vegetables%2C%20fruits%20and%20milk.%20Total%20fat%20intake%20should%20be%20less%20than%20or%20equal%20to%2030%20per%20cent%20energy%2C%20the%20guidelines%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20the%20limited%20availability%20and%20high%20cost%20of%20pulses%20and%20meat%2C%20a%20significant%20proportion%20of%20the%20Indian%20population%20relies%20heavily%20on%20cereals%2C%20resulting%20in%20poor%20intake%20of%20essential%20macronutrients%20(essential%20amino%20acids%20and%20essential%20fatty%20acids)%20and%20micronutrients%2C%20it%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELow%20intake%20of%20essential%20nutrients%20can%20disrupt%20metabolism%20and%20increase%20the%20risk%20of%20insulin%20resistance%20and%20associated%20disorders%20from%20a%20young%20age.%20Estimates%20show%20that%2056.4%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20total%20disease%20burden%20in%20India%20is%20due%20to%20unhealthy%20diets%2C%20it%20said.%20Healthy%20diets%20and%20physical%20activity%20can%20reduce%20a%20substantial%20proportion%20of%20coronary%20heart%20disease%20(CHD)%20and%20hypertension%20(HTN)%20and%20prevent%20up%20to%2080%20per%20cent%20of%20type%202%20diabetes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20significant%20proportion%20of%20premature%20deaths%20can%20be%20averted%20by%20following%20a%20healthy%20lifestyle%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20upsurge%20in%20the%20consumption%20of%20highly%20processed%20foods%20laden%20with%20sugars%20and%20fats%2C%20coupled%20with%20reduced%20physical%20activity%20and%20limited%20access%20to%20diverse%20foods%2C%20aggravated%20micronutrient%20deficiencies%20and%20obesity.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715263680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fagi66hq4_protein-supplements-protein-shake-generic-unsplash_625x300_09_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftop-medical-bodys-advisory-urges-people-t