er%20ally%20--%20the%20BJP%2C%20appears%20to%20have%20taken%20reports%20about%20his%20MLAs'%20secret%20meeting%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20with%20textbook%20equanimity.%20Switching%20parties%20is%20normal%20at%20election%20time%2C%20he%20told%20NDTV%20this%20evening.%20Asked%20about%20the%20possibility%20of%20an%20Operation%20Lotus%20by%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20is%20in%20a%20tight%20corner%20after%20three%20Independent%20MLAs%20pulled%20support%20to%20the%20government%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThen%20the%20people%20of%20Haryana%20will%20come%20to%20know%26quot%3B.%20Then%2C%20with%20a%20straight%20face%2C%20he%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BWho%20knows%2C%20even%20the%20BJP%20MLAs%20can%20switch%20sides%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20have%20said%20that%20four%20of%20the%20nine%20MLAs%20from%20Mr%20Chautala's%20JJP%20(Jannayak%20Janta%20Party)%20met%20the%20former%20BJP%20Chief%20Minister%20Manohar%20Lal%20Khattar%20this%20afternoon.%20AT%20the%20meeting%2C%20held%20in%20the%20Panipat%20house%20of%20state%20minister%20Mahipal%20Dhanda%2C%20the%20current%20political%20crisis%20was%20discussed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20had%20ended%20the%20alliance%20with%20Mr%20Chautala%2C%20a%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20in%20the%20Manohar%20Lal%20Khattar%20government%2C%20in%20March%2C%20as%20it%20effected%20a%20change%20of%20guard%20in%20the%20state%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%20Nayab%20Singh%20Saini%20was%20brought%20in%20to%20replace%20Mr%20Khattar%2C%20and%20Mr%20Chautala%2C%20after%20a%20failed%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20sharing%20deal%2C%20was%20shown%20the%20door.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20week%2C%20after%20the%20Independents%20pulled%20off%20support%20to%20the%20government%2C%20Mr%20Chautala%20responded.%20He%20promptly%20declared%20that%20the%20government%20is%20now%20in%20minority%20and%20asked%20the%20Governor%20for%20a%20floor%20test.%20Appearing%20at%20a%20press%20conference%20with%20leaders%20of%20the%20Opposition%20Congress%2C%20he%20also%20said%20he%20was%20ready%20to%20provide%20the%20Grand%20Old%20Party%20with%20outside%20support%20should%20they%20wish%20to%20form%20a%20new%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20asked%20about%20the%20JJP%20MLAs'%20meeting%20with%20Mr%20Khattar%2C%20Mr%20Chautala%20told%20NDTV%20this%20is%20was%20%26quot%3Bnot%20the%20time%20to%20worry%20about%20who%20is%20meeting%20whom%26quot%3B.%20The%20fact%20remains%20that%20the%20government%20is%20in%20minority%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20whip%20and%20expulsion%20were%20the%20standard%20means%20to%20deal%20with%20rebels%2C%20%26quot%3Bthis%20is%20the%20time%20of%20election%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20will%20switch%20parties.%20If%20someone%20has%20to%20switch%20parties%20we%20will%20come%20to%20know.%20Let%20it%20come%20out%20in%20public.%20Who%20knows%2C%20even%20the%20BJP%20MLAs%20can%20switch%20sides%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Haryana%20Assembly%2C%20with%2090%20seats%2C%20currently%20has%2088%20members%2C%20which%20brings%20the%20majority%20mark%20down%20to%2045.%20The%20BJP%20has%2040%20MLAs%2C%20including%20three%20Independent%20candidates%2C%20and%20is%20two%20short%20of%20majority.%20The%20Congress%20has%2030%20MLAs%20and%20three%20independent%20candidates%20supporting%20it.%20An%20undivided%20JJP%20would%20bring%20its%20numbers%20up%20to%2043%20MLAs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20scenario%20leaves%20two%20MLAs%20unaligned-one%20from%20the%20Haryana%20Lokhit%20Party%20and%20the%20other%20from%20the%20INLD.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20evening%2C%20INLD%20MLA%20Abhay%20Singh%20Chautala%20wrote%20to%20the%20Governor%2C%20saying%20if%20an%20assembly%20session%20cannot%20be%20called%2C%20President's%20Rule%20should%20immediately%20declared%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715263080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fc0cvak3g_dushyant-chautala-1200_625x300_17_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Feven-bjp-mlas-can-switch-sides-dushyant-chautala-on-prospect-of-split-5626212%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dushyant%20Chautala%2C%20the%20prime%20mover%20trying%20to%20pull%20down%20the%20Haryana%20government%20led%20by%20his%20former%20ally%2C%20the%20BJP%2C%20appears%20to%20have%20taken%20reports%20that%20around%20four%20of%20his%20nine%20MLAs%20had%20a%20secret%20meeting%20with%20the%20BJP%20this%20afternoon%2C%20with%20textbook%20equanimity.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Feven-bjp-mlas-can-switch-sides-dushyant-chautala-on-prospect-of-split-5626212%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Feven-bjp-mlas-can-switch-sides-dushyant-chautala-on-prospect-of-split-5626212%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Feven-bjp-mlas-can-switch-sides-dushyant-chautala-on-prospect-of-split-5626212%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Self-Styled%20%26quot%3BEunuch%20Maker%26quot%3B%20Jailed%20For%2022%20Years%20By%20UK%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20leader%20of%20a%20gang%20that%20carried%20out%20gruesome%20procedures%2C%20including%20castrations%2C%20has%20been%20jailed%20for%20life%20with%20a%20minimum%20term%20of%2022%20years.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20self-styled%20%26quot%3Beunuch%20maker%26quot%3B%20Marius%20Gustavson%20used%20to%20stream%20the%20mutilation%20online%20for%20paying%20customers.%20The%2046-year-old%20Norwegian%20ran%20a%20lucrative%20business%20in%20extreme%20body%20modifications.%20The%20outlet%20said%20that%20Gustavson%20has%20admitted%20to%20offences%2C%20including%20five%20counts%20of%20causing%20grievous%20bodily%20harm%20with%20intent.%20During%20the%20court%20hearing%2C%20he%20was%20described%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20lunatic%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3Ban%20arch-manipulator%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Ba%20butcher%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20pay-per-view%20website%20advertised%20services%2C%20including%20freezing%20of%20limbs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20videos%20show%20Gustavson%20and%20his%20accomplices%20performing%20extreme%20body%20modifications%20on%20apparently%20willing%20volunteers%20in%20hotel%20rooms%20and%20flats%20in%20London.%20As%20per%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fuk-england-london-68977469%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20some%20of%20them%20were%20as%20young%20as%2016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20legal%20team%20said%20while%20defending%20him%20at%20the%20Central%20Criminal%20Court%20in%20London%20that%20Gustavson%20only%20wanted%20to%20%26quot%3Bput%20a%20smile%26quot%3B%20on%20faces%20of%20those%20people%20who%20suffered%2C%20like%20him%2C%20from%20body%20integrity%20dysphoria%20(BID).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20prosecutors%20accused%20Gustavson%20of%20carrying%20out%20%26quot%3Bhuman%20butchery%26quot%3B%20done%20for%20sexual%2C%20rather%20than%20psychiatric%2C%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20suggest%20that%20diagnosis%20-%20if%20it%20exists%20-%20may%20explain%20why%20it%20is%20Mr%20Gustavson%20acted%20as%20he%20did%20to%20have%20his%20own%20body%20maimed%20and%20mutilated%2C%20but%20does%20not%20explain%20why%20he%20made%20a%20lucrative%20business%20out%20of%20mutilating%20others%2C%26quot%3B%20barrister%20Caroline%20Carberry%20KC%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGustavson%20earned%20300%2C000%20pounds%20(Rs%203.13%20crore)%20from%20his%20website%20and%20had%2022%2C841%20visitors%20from%20across%20the%20globe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20subscribers%20even%20paid%20100%20pounds%20(Rs%2010%2C000)%20yearly%20subscription%20for%20VIP%20status.%20The%20victims%20were%20promised%20money%20from%20the%20video%20revenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20also%20%26quot%3Bclear%20evidence%26quot%3B%20of%20cannibalism%20by%20Gustavson%2C%20the%20prosecution%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20network%20was%20destroyed%20by%20a%20brave%20victim%2C%20who%20has%20not%20been%20named%20for%20legal%20reasons.%20The%20participant%20told%20the%20police%20about%20the%20procedures%20carried%20out%20on%20him%20-%20and%20provided%20a%20USB%20stick%20that%20contained%205%2C000%20WhatsApp%20messages%2C%20100%20images%20and%20a%20number%20of%20videos.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715262780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F8bo63418_marius-gustavson-mutilator-1200_625x300_09_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fself-styled-eunuch-maker-jailed-for-22-years-by-uk-court-5626333%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%2046-year-old%20Norwegian%20ran%20a%20lucrative%20business%20in%20extreme%20body%20modifications%20and%20even%20streamed%20the%20procedures%20online.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fself-styled-eunuch-maker-jailed-for-22-years-by-uk-court-5626333%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fself-styled-eunuch-maker-jailed-for-22-years-by-uk-court-5626333%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fself-styled-eunuch-maker-jailed-for-22-years-by-uk-court-5626333%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chinese%20Executive%20Asks%20Employees%20To%20%26quot%3BKeep%20Phone%20On%2024%20Hours%26quot%3B%2C%20Slammed%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWork-life%20balance%20is%20a%20key%20part%20of%20a%20productive%20work%20environment%2C%20which%20can%20improve%20your%20physical%20and%20mental%20health.%20Recently%2C%20a%20top%20PR%20executive%20at%20Chinese%20internet%20giant%20Baidu%20sparked%20public%20outrage%20after%20her%20controversial%20videos%20glorifying%20overworking%20culture%20went%20viral%20on%20Chinese%20social%20media%2C%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcz4x5nnpe80o%5C%22%3EBBC%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQu%20Jing%2C%20Baidu's%20vice%20president%20and%20head%20of%20the%20public%20relations%20department%2C%20posted%20four%20videos%20on%20TikTok's%20Chinese%20sister%20Douyin%2C%20endorsing%20a%20tough%20workplace%20culture.%C2%A0In%20the%20first%20video%2C%20she%20criticized%20employees%20who%20refused%20to%20go%20on%20long%20business%20trips%2C%20stating%20she%20had%20%26quot%3Bno%20obligation%20to%20know%20if%20employees%20are%20crying.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20do%20I%20have%20to%20consider%20the%20family%20of%20an%20employee%3F%20I%20am%20not%20her%20mother-in-law!%26quot%3B%20she%20asked%20in%20one%20video.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20are%20not%20satisfied%20with%20your%20job%2C%20you%20can%20resign.%20I%20will%20approve%20it%20immediately%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20video%2C%20she%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20work%20in%20public%20relations%2C%20don't%20expect%20weekends%20off.%20Keep%20your%20phone%20on%2024%20hours%20a%20day%2C%20always%20ready%20to%20respond.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20threatened%20retaliation%20against%20subordinates%20who%20complained%20about%20her%20management.%20%26quot%3BI%20can%20make%20it%20impossible%20for%20you%20to%20find%20a%20job%20in%20this%20industry%20with%20just%20a%20short%20essay%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20videos%20spread%20like%20wildfire%20with%20users%20slamming%20her%20for%20aggressive%20and%20insensitive%20approach.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''In%20her%20voice%20and%20her%20tone%2C%20there's%20deep%20indifference%20to%20and%20lack%20of%20empathy%20for%20the%20common%20plight%20of%20her%20colleagues.%20This%20is%20what%20the%20bosses%20are%20thinking%2C%20and%20she%20was%20merely%20saying%20it%20out%20aloud%2C''%20a%20China%20tech%20analyst%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2024%2F05%2F09%2Ftech%2Fchina-qu-jing-baidu-pr-backlash-hnk-intl%2Findex.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ECNN%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20widespread%20public%20anger%2C%20the%20four%20videos%20posted%20by%20Ms%20Jing%20were%20deleted.%20Posting%20an%20apology%2C%20she%20said%20her%20videos%20did%20not%20represent%20Baidu's%20stance%20and%20that%20she%20had%20not%20sought%20the%20company's%20consent%20before%20posting%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-component-name%3D%5C%22paragraph%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%22cms.cnn.com%2F_components%2Fparagraph%2Finstances%2Fclvz3r4u6000q3b6ju72j7tkq%40published%5C%22%20data-analytics-observe%3D%5C%22off%5C%22%20data-editable%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%20data-article-gutter%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E''I%20have%20carefully%20read%20all%20the%20opinions%20and%20comments%20from%20various%20platforms%2C%20and%20many%20criticisms%20are%20very%20pertinent.%20I%20deeply%20reflect%20on%20and%20humbly%20accept%20them%2C''%20Ms%C2%A0%20Jing%20wrote%20on%20WeChat%2C%C2%A0China's%20most%20popular%20social%20media%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20apologise%20that%20the%20inappropriate%20videos%20led%20to%20the%20public's%20misunderstanding%20of%20my%20company's%20values%20and%20corporate%20culture.%C2%A0There%20were%20many%20inappropriate%20and%20unsuitable%20points%20in%20the%20videos%2C%20which%20led%20to%20misunderstandings%20about%20the%20company's%20values%20and%20corporate%20culture%2C%20causing%20serious%20harm%20I%20will%20learn%20from%20my%20mistakes%20improve%20the%20way%20I%20communicate%2C%20and%20care%20more%20for%20my%20colleagues%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715262720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-03%2F97tkm84_baidu-generic-reuters_625x300_16_March_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fkeep-your-phone-on-24-hours-chinese-executive-sparks-outrage-after-she-glorifies-overwork-5625934%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20v