9CI%20started%20with%20growing%201%20kg%20of%20microgreens%20at%20home%20and%20now%20my%20farm%20can%20grow%2050%20kg%20of%20microgreens%20in%20one%20harvest%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Aditi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20microgreens%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFalling%20between%20the%20categories%20of%20a%20baby%20green%20and%20a%20sprout%2C%20microgreens%20are%20nutrition-packed%20herbs%20and%20vegetables.%20According%20to%20a%20%3Cem%3EHealthline%3C%2Fem%3Earticle%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20often%20contain%20higher%20nutrient%20levels%20than%20more%20mature%20vegetable%20greens.%20This%20makes%20them%20a%20good%20addition%20to%20any%20diet.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAditi%20believes%20that%20India%20still%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20knowledge%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F306361%2Fwhy-is-makhana-expensive-lotus-seeds-fox-nuts-grown-in-bihar-gi-tagged-watch-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eabout%20the%20superfood%3C%2Fa%3E%20microgreens.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20am%20at%20the%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20market%20or%20at%20pop-ups%20and%20am%20interacting%20with%20the%20people%2C%20I%20realise%20that%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20unawareness%20among%20them.%20Including%20these%20little%20pockets%20of%20nutrition%20in%20your%20daily%20diet%20can%20really%20do%20wonders%20for%20your%20body.%20They%20contain%20large%20amounts%20of%20vitamins%20B%2C%20K%20and%20C%2C%20folic%20acid%2C%20magnesium%2C%20minerals%20and%20antioxidants%2C%20which%20have%20immense%20health%20benefits%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20you%20consume%2020-30%20gm%20of%20a%20microgreen%20vegetable%2C%20you%20are%20eating%20double%20the%20nutritional%20value%20of%20the%20same%20amount%20of%20regular%20vegetables%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Ci