outhern%20Health%20Improvement%20Samity)%20started%20in%201980%20%E2%80%94%20when%20Wohab%2C%20a%20lawyer%2C%20and%20Pal%2C%20a%20teacher%2C%20bonded%20over%20their%20intentions%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F278313%2Fsundarbans-hingalganj-island-english-medium-school-inspiring-teacher-kolkata%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echampion%20change%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20their%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98People%20were%20dying%20in%20front%20of%20my%20eyes%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E380%20mm%20of%20rainfall%20in%2024%20hours.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWest%20Bengal%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20been%20able%20to%20forget%2027%20September%201978.%20Thousands%20died%2C%20starved%20and%20were%20left%20homeless%20as%20the%20torrential%20rain%20washed%20away%20entire%20houses.%20Wohab%2C%20who%20lived%20in%20Howrah%20at%20the%20time%2C%20recalls%20the%20harrowing%20ordeal.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20heartbreaking%20to%20watch%20people%20and%20their%20cattle%20drowning%20in%20the%20water.%20All%20around%2C%20flood%20victims%20were%20taking%20shelter%20in%20other%E2%80%99s%20homes%20and%20schools%2C%20and%20even%20climbing%20up%20trees%20to%20avoid%20drowning.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20one%20knew%20what%20the%20next%20week%2C%20much%20less%20the%20next%20few%20days%2C%20would%20bring.%20It%20was%20in%20this%20chaos%20that%20Wohab%20watched%20as%20a%20man%2C%20who%20seemed%20like%20a%20foreigner%2C%20was%20rowing%20his%20boat%20through%20the%20floodwater%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F329667%2Fpalghar-kiran-kamdar-free-homemade-khichdi-for-patients-hospital-parkinson-disease%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edistributing%20food%20packets%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20people.%20This%20attracted%20the%20lawyer%20who%20was%20working%20as%20secretary%20to%20a%20village-level%20g