0developed%20geo%20treks%20for%20exploration.%20Additionally%2C%20we%E2%80%99ve%20established%20butterfly%20spots%20where%20visitors%20can%20learn%20about%20the%20forest%20and%20river%20ecosystems.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESetting%20up%20and%20running%20an%20ecotourism%20centre%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20area%20became%20an%20eco-tourism%20centre%2C%20Vikas%20informs%20that%20the%20place%20was%20a%20breeding%20ground%20for%20them%20and%20dacoits.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20with%20planting%20trees%20in%20the%20areas%20and%20improving%20the%20place%E2%80%99s%20greenery.%20We%20also%20set%20up%20habitats%20for%20birds%20and%20butterflies.%20Although%20the%20place%20had%20many%20trees%2C%20we%20started%20to%20plant%20more%20and%20build%20the%20place%20around%20the%20trees.%20The%20design%20was%20such%20that%20it%20did%20not%20disrupt%20the%20existing%20biodiversity%20of%20the%20place%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVikas%20wanted%20to%20create%20and%20attract%20more%20tourists%20to%20the%20area%2C%20and%20he%20also%20wanted%20to%20raise%20awareness%20about%20eco%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F298606%2Fecosphere-encourages-sustainable-tourism-in-spiti-solar-power-homestays-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresponsible%20tourism.%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20has%20been%20in%20the%20history%20of%20the%20forest%20department%20to%20involve%20locals%20in%20the%20work.%20From%20helping%20with%20maintaining%20the%20forests%20to%20setting%20up%20such%20projects%20to%20rescuing%20wildlife%2C%20it%20has%20been%20a%20tradition%20for%20the%20department%20to%20seek%20help%20from%20the%20local%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20this%20tradition%2C%20Vikas%20mapped%20out%20a%20plan%20that%20would%20help%20the%20local%20community%20grow.%C2%A