0job%20to%20run%20a%20saree%20shop.%20My%20family%20also%20kept%20asking%20me%20about%20my%20daily%20progress.%20I%20had%20no%20answers%20to%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoving%20to%20Chennai%20was%20a%20challenging%20chapter%20of%20his%20life.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20surviving%20on%20loans%20from%20friends.%20I%20was%20living%20in%20a%20small%20room%20on%20rent%20and%20survived%20on%20one%20meal%20a%20day%20to%20save%20money.%20There%20were%20days%20when%20I%20wanted%20to%20quit%3B%20I%20wanted%20to%20cry%20and%20go%20back%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Ankush%20remembered%20all%20the%20promises%20of%20an%20opulent%20life%20that%20he%20made%20to%20his%20parents.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20to%20find%20ways%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20a%20mobile%20app%2C%20Ankush%20designed%20a%20website%20for%20Deeva%20and%20listed%20the%20most%20buying%20categories%20on%20the%20homepage.%20%E2%80%9CBy%20this%20time%2C%20I%20had%20understood%20that%20my%20customers%20were%20office-going%20women%20in%20the%20age%20group%20of%2025%20to%2045%20years%20who%20wanted%20to%20wear%20good%20quality%20sarees%20on%20a%20daily%20basis%20by%20investing%20Rs%202%2C000%20to%20Rs%202%2C500.%20I%20started%20sourcing%20more%20such%20sarees%20from%20manufacturers%20and%20advertised%20them%20on%20the%20homepage%20for%20easy%20search%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20boost%20sales%2C%20Ankush%20also%20outsourced%20to%20a%20digital%20marketing%20company%20that%20helped%20advertise%20the%20sarees.%20%E2%80%9CSoon%20after%2C%20I%20started%20getting%20sales%20through%20social%20media.%20I%20got%20my%20first%20boost%20in%20April-May%202022%20when%20I%20made%20sales%20of%20Rs%2015%2C000%20in%20one%20day.%20This%20was%20when%20I%20decided%20to%20come%20back%20to%20Himachal%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20he%20returned%20to%20his%20village%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20looking%20back.%20Today%2C%20he%20has%20established%20a%20multi-crore%20company%20based%20out%20of%20Bangana%20that%20sells%20sarees%20across%20the%20country%20in%2050%20categories%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Patola%2C%20Kanjivaram%2C%20Chanderi%2C%20Banarasi%20silk%2C%20and%20Chiffon%20sarees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC4mbhbOPt4v%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC4mbhbOPt4v%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC4mbhbOPt4v%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Ankush%20R%20Barjata%20(%40ankushxbusiness)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnkush%20has%20established%20a%20core%20team%20of%2030%20people%20from%20his%20village.%20He%20has%20partnered%20with%20at%20least%20500%20manufacturers%20across%20the%20country.%20This%20partnership%20has%20been%20a%20win-win%20for%20Ankush%20as%20well%20as%20small%20manufacturers%20who%20have%20observed%20a%20boost%20of%20at%20least%20five%20times%20in%20their%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20his%20manufacturers%2C%20Himanshu%20Jain%2C%20who%20has%20been%20associated%20with%20Ankush%20for%20the%20past%20year%20and%20a%20half%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%20we%20had%20to%20work%20on%20credit%20with%20offline%20distributors.%20This%20meant%20that%20we%E2%80%99d%20get%20payments%20only%20after%2030%20to%2045%20days.%20They%20would%20also%20buy%20sarees%20in%20bulk%20and%20there%20was%20no%20surety%20if%20all%20sarees%20would%20be%20sold.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%2C%20they%20would%20return%20to%20us%20after%20a%20month%20or%20so%20and%20dump%20all%20the%20unsold%20sarees.%20The%20onus%20to%20sell%20these%20would%20fall%20on%20us.%20But%20with%20Deeva%2C%20we%20get%20orders%20only%20after%20the%20consumer%20has%20placed%20an%20order%2C%20and%20we%20get%20payments%20in%207%20to%2010%20days.%20Here%2C%20my%20income%20has%20also%20increased%20by%2025%20percent%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20to%20make%20Deeva%20a%20big%20brand%2C%20Ankush%20wanted%20to%20appear%20on%20Shark%20Tank%20India.%20Even%20though%20he%20could%20not%20make%20it%20to%20season%202%2C%20he%20made%20a%20lasting%20impression%20on%20the%20%E2%80%98sharks%E2%80%99%20in%20season%203.%20The%20impact%20of%20the%20episode%20was%20so%20enormous%20that%20he%20observed%20a%20boost%20of%20six%20times%20in%20his%20business%2C%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERooted%20in%20his%20village%2C%20Ankush%20now%20aims%20to%20make%20a%20business%20of%20Rs%20150%20crore%2C%20enter%20into%20export%20in%20at%20least%2010%20countries%2C%20and%20open%20offline%20stores%20in%20the%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20do%20not%20feel%20I%20have%20achieved%20very%20big.%20It%20was%20through%20my%20grandfather%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20that%20we%20started%20getting%20meals%20three%20times%20a%20day.%20My%20parents%20worked%20hard%20so%20that%20we%20could%20wear%20decent%20clothes.%20I%20just%20want%20to%20give%20whatever%20best%20life%20I%20can%20to%20my%20parents%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRecently%2C%20I%20gifted%20a%20seven-seater%20car%20to%20my%20father.%20Currently%2C%20we%20are%20building%20our%20dream%20house%20with%20a%20helipad%20and%20rooftop%20swimming%20pool%20in%20Himachal%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CAlthough%20these%20are%20materialistic%20things%2C%20having%20a%20%3Cem%3Ebada%20ghar%2C%20badi%20gaadi%20%3C%2Fem%3E(big%20house%2C%20big%20car)%20are%20dreams%20of%20a%20lower-middle%20income%20family.%20In%20eight%20months%2C%20I%20will%20move%20to%20our%20new%20home%20with%20my%20family.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat.%20All%20photos%3A%20Ankush%20Barjata.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714745043000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FAnkush-1714728877.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D348898%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ankush%20Barjata%20founded%20an%20online%20saree%20platform%20named%20'Deeva'%20from%20a%20small%20Himachal%20village.%20His%20journey%2C%20rooted%20in%20his%20family's%20clothing%20legacy%2C%20was%20driven%20by%20a%20vision%20to%20provide%20a%20better%20life%20for%20his%20family.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F348898%2Fsaree-startup-online-business-ankush-barjata-founded-deeva-buy-shark-tank-india-bangana-himachal%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20An%20Architect%20is%20Using%20Stationery%20to%20Prevent%209000%20Kg%20Cotton%20Waste%20From%20Reaching%20Landfills%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERashi%20Agarwal%E2%80%99s%20final%20year%20of%20college%20was%20incredibly%20enriching.%20She%20embarked%20on%20a%20nationwide%20journey%20to%20explore%20traditional%20