t%20to%20note%20that%20they%20have%20a%20life%20waiting%20for%20them%20back%20in%20their%20respective%20villages.%20What%20happens%20to%20that%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20where%20Access%20Life%E2%80%99s%20Emotional%20and%20Psychological%20Support%20(EPS)%20programme%20comes%20in.%20It%20equips%20families%20with%20practical%20ways%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20distress%20created%20by%20the%20disease.%20It%E2%80%99s%20about%20keeping%20the%20children%20engaged%20with%20educational%20sessions%20so%20that%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20miss%20out%20on%20school%2C%20and%20teaching%20the%20parents%20new%20skills%20that%20could%20be%20a%20source%20of%20livelihood%20when%20they%20return%20to%20their%20respective%20hometowns%20after%20their%20child%E2%80%99s%20long%20treatment%2C%20the%20duo%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPointing%20to%20one%20example%2C%20Ankeet%20recalls%20the%20example%20of%20a%20parent%20who%20used%20to%20run%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F259515%2Findian-food-recipes-pakora-map-of-india-cuisine-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Epuri%20bhajiya%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3E(a%20fast%20food%20stall)%20stall%20in%20Siliguri%2C%20West%20Bengal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20he%20came%20to%20live%20at%20our%20centre%20for%20his%20child%E2%80%99s%20treatment%20(which%20lasted%20six%20months)%2C%20he%20had%20to%20sell%20his%20cart%20back%20home.%20He%20was%20worried%20about%20what%20would%20happen%20to%20his%20livelihood.%20But%20during%20his%20time%20here%2C%20he%20learnt%20how%20to%20make%20%3Cem%3Evada%20pav%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20started%20selling!%20The%20business%20was%20a%20huge%20success%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGirish%20pitches%20in%20with%20another%20heartwarming%20story.%20%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20parents%20was%20a%20soldier%20who%20quit%20and%20came%20to%20our%20Mumbai%20centre%20when%20his%20child%20was%20admitted.%20But%20in%20the%20weeks%20that%20followed%2C%20he%20saw%20how%20well%20his%20son%20was%20being%20cared%20for%20at%20the%20centre.%20That%20enabled%20him%20to%20go%20back%20to%20his%20duty%20peacefully.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20duo%20encourages%20both%20parents%20to%20stay%20with%20the%20child%20at%20the%20centre%2C%20they%20are%20aware%20that%20this%20is%20not%20always%20possible%20and%20are%20always%20willing%20to%20make%20exceptions.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20there%20is%20a%20family%20that%20has%20two%20kids%20and%20one%20is%20admitted%20here%20and%20the%20other%20is%20an%20infant%2C%20we%20ask%20the%20family%20to%20bring%20both%20kids%20so%20they%20can%20all%20live%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20Girish%20shares.%20They%20go%20to%20great%20lengths%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20comfort%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327071%2Fvaranasi-ias-officer-himanshu-nagpal-mission-muskaan-reunites-lost-children-with-families%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20families%3C%2Fa%3E%20trumps%20everything%20else.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20they%20navigate%20this%20challenge%2C%20it%20is%20reassuring%20to%20know%20that%20someone%20is%20looking%20out%20for%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECancer%20warrants%20a%20certain%20trepidation%2C%20a%20certain%20tiptoeing%2C%20a%20certain%20foreboding.%20But%20the%20laughter%20and%20happy%20chatter%20at%20the%20Access%20Life%20centres%2C%20disagree.%20For%20anyone%20looking%20in%2C%20there%20is%20only%20hope%20to%20be%20found%20here.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20donate%20to%20their%20cause%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.accesslife.org%2Fdonation%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714733955000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fcancer-centre-1714468603.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D348647%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ankeet%20Dave%20and%20Girish%20Nair%2C%20founders%20of%20Access%20Life%2C%20were%20deeply%20affected%20by%20the%20pain%20of%20infants%20undergoing%20chemotherapy.%20They%20started%20helping%20the%20patients%E2%80%99%20families%20with%20shelter%2C%20food%20and%20transport%20in%20major%20Indian%20cities.%20This%20is%20their%20story%20of%20empathy%20and%20hard%20work.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F348647%2Fcancer-shelter-in-india-access-life-ankeet-dave-girish-nair-children-paediatric-care-in-mumbai%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20to%20Identify%20Fake%20%E2%80%98Paneer%E2%80%99%20At%20Home%3F%203%20Simple%20Tests%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFor%20vegetarians%2C%20%3Cem%3Epaneer%20%3C%2Fem%3E(cottage%20cheese)%20is%20touted%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20best%20sources%20of%20protein%20and%20forms%20an%20important%20part%20of%20the%20daily%20diet.%20However%2C%20consumers%20are%20turning%20wary%20about%20buying%20this%20soft%20cheese%20due%20to%20reports%20of%20adulteration.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20April%202024%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F348030%2Fmdh-everest-sambhar-masala-fssai-guidelines-food-safety-ethylene-oxide-fish-curry-masala-singapore-hong-kong%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFood%20Safety%20and%20Standards%20Authority%20of%20India%20(FSSAI)%3C%2Fa%3E%20tests%20found%20that%2047%20out%20of%C2%A0168%20%3Cem%3Epaneer%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3Ekhoya%20%3C%2Fem%3Eproducts%20were%20contaminated.%20Earlier%20this%20year%2C%20a%20whopping%201%2C300%20kg%20of%20fake%20%3Cem%3Epaneer%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewas%20discovered%20and%20disposed%20of%20by%20authorities%20al